# Underline the verbs in the below sentences.

1. Susan ran to the school.
2. Sharks swim in the ocean.
3. Sam walked to his school everyday.
4. Ram washed his toy car in the rain.
5. Hari sipped his tea slowly.
6. Pradeep tossed the ball. 
7. Some flowers bloom in the evening.
8. Bees build their nest on the tree.
9. Ramya likes to study in the morning.
10. Children painted beautiful pictures. 
